data.description: Welcome to WalnutHurst! This historical home is a small piece of paradise with next level privacy and exceptional views. This is the dream home you've been waiting for. It has it all! The acreage, a 5,756 sq foot home with 6 bedrooms and 4 full bathrooms, a total of 6 outbuildings that can be used for various interests, a stream and a fenced in pasture for animals. The sellers have put 120k of updates into the home. All it needs is your finishing touches! 10 minutes from Deer Creek!! Don't miss out on this once in a lifetime opportunity!Seller is willing to help with rate buy downs, closing costs or allowance for the flooring!!!
